channel.title: Dosis Network Down :: SANS Holiday Hack Challenge 2025
channel.description: Objective Difficulty: 2/5 Drop by JJ’s 24-7 for a network rescue and help restore the holiday cheer. What is the WiFi password found in the router’s config? Janusz Jasinski mission statement Hello! I’m JJ. I like rock, metal, and punk music. That’s all I have to say about that. I accept BTC. Skeletor is my hero Alright then. Those bloody gnomes ‘ave proper messed about with the neighborhood’s wifi - changed the admin password, probably mucked up all the settings, the lot.
